involved in any aspect of the operation of th e rating systems which it reviews in 
accordance with paragraph 1(a);

point_Article_17_Paragraph_2_Point_(e).text:
the internal audit or the other comparable independent auditing unit is 
independent from the personnel and management responsible for originating or 
renewing exposures and reports directly to senior management;

